{"tid":1558910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 民陣大遊行- 連儂牆要人","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:23:43.000Z","uid":299093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc358866ce7577446602741f01581db40b473a3","tid":1558910,"uid":299093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"今日經過見到沙田同石硤尾連儂牆都被撕得乾乾淨淨，唔知其他區係咪有同樣情況，係時候貼番啲新嘢落去啦！<br />\n<br />\n民陣大遊行<br />\n已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n日期: 9月15日 (星期日)<br />\n時間: 下午3時<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n<br />\n要用所有方式谷到二百萬人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxM4NOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfxM4NOw.jpg&h=d0e43262&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K30dF8x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK30dF8x.jpg&h=6c50b593&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2MMgGT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2MMgGT.png&h=c901c12b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VTyZBGT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVTyZBGT.png&h=ecfb1ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpHPetA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpHPetA.png&h=ce030872&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDJe91Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDJe91Z.png&h=a9466d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"452f7092a0b3e16f1945827e7b8e6c5c763351ee","tid":1558910,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"從沒放棄過失敗~"},{"pid":"221f0bdc5e4584f7a54213647169ad559d89444a","tid":1558910,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"[911恐襲] 除左瘋狂Twitter，仲有樣 好 撚 重 要 既野要一齊做！！！<br />\n